ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/5/02 2:02:05 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9728.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Remove Greater Curse</span><hr size=1> Seems fairly rare now,  we got 5-7 within 2 weeks of SoL and IIRC we haven't seen one since. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usmokingdorf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Smoking Dorf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/5/02 4:45:55 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9728.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Remove Greater Curse</span><hr size=1> Quite rare indeed. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ujondinsottovoce.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jondin Sottovoce</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.supernet.net/~langston/noteicon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/5/02 6:30:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9728.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Remove Greater Curse</span><hr size=1> Mind Burrowers in Ahkeva drop it I belive. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uadvilan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Advilan</A>&nbsp